com.mattrader.common

Class OrderCom

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mattrader.common.OrderCom

  • public final class OrderCom
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will model an order, giving information on the status (error, pending, received, executed, cancelled, confirmation_needed) and handling data specific of the order.
